Abdomen – Gray with the usual silver tesselation and slightly golden microtomentum in lateral; T 1 + 2–3 without median marginal seta, T 4 with a pair of median marginal setae; ST 2 with long and dense black setae. ST 5 with scattered black thin setae, posterior margin with a shallow concavity (
Fig. 44
